snippet.title: Andhra King Taluka Teaser | Ram Pothineni | Upendra | Mahesh Babu P | Bhagyashri Borse
snippet.description:
Presenting the Energetic teaser of #AndhraKingTaluka 

Andhra King Taluka - A BIOPIC OF A FAN is a Telugu Film starring Ram Pothineni, Upendra and Bhagyashri Borse. The film is written and directed by Mahesh Babu P and produced by Naveen Yerneni, Y. Ravi Shankar under Mythri Movie Makers. Music is by Vivek & Mervin. The film brings untold emotions between a fan and a superstar onto the big screens on 28th November worldwide.

#AndhraKingTalukaTeaser #AndhraKingTaluka #RamPothineni #Upendra #MaheshBabuP #BhagyashriBorse #RaoRamesh #MuraliSharma #Satya #RahulRamakrishna #NaveenYerneni #YRaviShankar #MythriMovieMakers #LatestTeluguMovies2025

Presenting the lyrical of ''Onde Ondu Sala'' from the movie ''The Devil'' starring Challenging Star Darshan, Rachana Rai and others. Shri Jaimatha Combines, in association with Saregama a Yoodlee Films, presents the much-awaited film The Devil.

Produced by: J. Jayamma, Prakash Veer & Saregama
Directed by: Prakash Veer
Executive Producer: Thashwini Veer
Dialogue: Kanthraj S.S
Costumes: Chethan & Thashwini Veer
Line Producers: Indo Bangkok Films
Direction Department: Mohan Malagi, M.S. Abishaik, B. Thimme Gowdaa, Purnima Deshpande, Mallik R, Bharath, Chandrakumar, Yuvraj Hemanth

Still Photography: Kadur Raghu, Kadur Yogi
Lyrical Video: Gowtham Raj (Single Frame Studio)
Poster Design: Ashwin Ramesh (Win Designs)
PRO: Sudhindra Venkatesh
Digital PR: Pavan Venkatesh

Onde Ondu Sala Sothu Bide Nee
Onde Ondu Maathu Aadade
Bendu Bendu Ninna Daahadolage
Noora Ondu Aase Moodide......

Edeya Kenakone

snippet.title: Kantara Chapter 1 Hindi Success Trailer | Rishab Shetty, Rukmini Vasanth | Hombale films
snippet.description:
From Hombale Films ‚Äî the makers behind KGF: Chapter 1 & 2 and Salaar ‚Äî and the visionary, National Award‚Äìwinning Filmmaker and Actor Rishab Shetty, comes the official trailer for Kantara: A Legend ‚Äì Chapter 1. 

Starring Rishab Shetty as Berme, Rukmini Vasanth as Kanakavathi, and Gulshan Devaiah as Kulashekara, supported by a formidable ensemble cast.With a soul-stirring score by B. Ajaneesh Loknath and produced by Vijay Kiragandur under Hombale Films, Kantara: A Legend ‚Äì Chapter 1 promises visceral action, haunting melodies and a saga that will echo through generations. 

Witness India's Divine Epic on Screens this 2 October 2025.

Whether it‚Äôs the bold delivery by Sabba or the electrifying hook line brought alive by Gurlez Akhtar, ‚Äú32 Dand‚Äù is made to rule your playlists and dominate dance floors.

A must-listen for fans of Punjabi pop songs, this track reflects today‚Äôs youth culture‚Äîfull of attitude, style, and non-stop energy. If you're into Punjabi beats, duet songs, or just looking for a fresh 2025 Punjabi hit, ‚Äú32 Dand‚Äù is your next go-to anthem.
